org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel

Class ClassifierEvaluationImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.ytex.kernel.ClassifierEvaluationImporter

  • public class ClassifierEvaluationImporter
extends java.lang.Object
    parse classifier evaluation results. expect input data files to classifier in working directory. expect output in dir option or subdirectories thereof. expect an options.properties in each directory that contains classifier output. See ClassifierEvaluationImporter() for a list of options in options.properties. You can override options via system properties (java -D options).

      • importDirectory

        public void importDirectory(CommandLine line)
                     throws java.io.IOException
        Expect directory with subdirectories for each evaluation. Subdirectories must contain following in order for results to be processed:
        • model.txt: libsvm model trained on training set
        • predict.txt: libsvm predictions on test set
        • options.properties: libsvm command line options

        line -
        Throws:
